â•‘                                                              â•‘
â•šâ•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

SCROLL DOWN FOR MORE...

Features we covered today:
1.  spin      - Animated spinners while commands run
2.  style     - Style text with colors, borders, padding
3.  confirm   - Yes/No prompts
4.  choose    - Selection from a list
5.  input     - Single-line text input
6.  filter    - Fuzzy filtering of lists
7.  write     - Multi-line text input
8.  format    - Render markdown
9.  table     - Display tabular data
10. join      - Combine styled elements
11. log       - Structured logging
12. file      - File picker
13. pager     - Scroll through content

More at: https://github.com/charmbracelet/gum
